_aChangeLog.text: Fixed a trigger that was sticking out in the cavern area.
Removed collison on the cavern displacements (This was done a few hours after the initial update after it was brought to my attention)

_sText:
The second map in the conquest series

A casual run is about 3 minutes or so, but there's a ton of skips and you can fly through the map.

Sad Rainbow made bonus 1 which can be found at the end teleporter. It's a 30 second or so speed run map. There is also a little bonus 2 within the main map.

Have fun
